thread.title: Diane
thread.title_full: Curtains on the Net reviewed by Diane

author: Diane
title: Diane
text: Curtains were well made with good quality fabric that was close to the colour represented on the website and within the expected time period. My only gripe is that I didn't receive the email confirming the goods were on their way and shortly after emailing an enquiry the parcel arrived.
